data.description: Charming single-family home nestled in the sought-after community of Preserves at Tradition. Built in 2022, this gem offers 4 bedrooms and 2 baths with complete impact windows and doors. Beautiful lake view that can be enjoyed from multiple vantage points. The master suite offers a private oasis with a well-appointed en-suite bathroom, while the additional bedrooms are generously sized and versatile, accommodating various needs. The open-concept layout seamlessly connects the kitchen to the inviting living areas, allowing for seamless interaction with family and friends. Community offers a splash pad, dog park, butterfly garden and playground. Conveniently located to 95 and the Turnpike, schools, shopping, and dining, this property embraces the essence of Florida living.
